OL,3,CWest Midlands Police Commissioner wins
OL,4,Clegal challenge against power transfer
OL,6,FA judge has now ruled in Mr Foster's
OL,7,Ffavour, concluding the Home Office had
OL,8,Fnot provided sufficient information
OL,9,Fwhen consulting over its plans.
OL,11,FMr Foster, who previously branded the
OL,12,Fplans as a "hostile takeover" and a
OL,13,F"cynical power grab", argued the
OL,14,Fpowers transfer decision should be
OL,15,Freversed, claiming there were failings
OL,16,Fin a public consultation.
