OL,6,FAt a hearing earlier this month, his
OL,7,Flawyers argued the Home Office's
OL,8,Fconsultation was "no more than a tick
OL,9,Fbox exercise", with having a "closed
OL,10,Fmind" on the issue.
OL,12,FThe Home Office told the court in
OL,13,FLondon the transfer decision was taken
OL,14,F"with an open mind following a lawful
OL,15,Fconsultation and with regard to
OL,16,Frelevant information".
OL,18,FIn his 23-page written ruling, Mr
OL,19,FJustice Swift said:
