OL,6,F"The Home Secretary did not, when
OL,7,Fconsulting, provide sufficient
OL,8,Finformation to permit intelligent and
OL,9,Finformed response."
OL,11,FElected PCCs:
OL,13,FEvery force area in England and Wales
OL,14,Fis represented by a Police and Crime
OL,15,FCommissioner except London, Manchester
OL,16,Fand West Yorkshire, where the mayor
OL,17,Fholds the responsibility instead.
OL,19,FPCC functions are also due to transfer
OL,20,Fto the South Yorkshire mayor in May.
