OL,6,F"The Home Secretary and the Mayor have
OL,7,Fwasted everyone's time and tax payers'
OL,8,Fmoney"
OL,10,FIn a statement, Simon Foster said:
OL,12,F"I am pleased that the people of the
OL,13,FWest Midlands will now have the right
OL,14,Fto vote for a democratically elected
OL,15,Fand directly accountable Police and
OL,16,FCrime Commissioner at the election on
OL,17,F2 May 2024, whose one and only top
OL,18,Fpriority is preventing, tackling and
OL,19,Freducing crime.
