OL,3,CWest Midlands Police Commissioner wins
OL,4,Clegal challenge against power transfer
OL,6,F"I brought this claim for Judicial
OL,7,FReview to fulfil my Manifesto pledge
OL,8,Fto the people of the West Midlands,
OL,9,Fthe commitment in my Police and Crime
OL,10,FPlan and to defend democracy, the rule
OL,11,Fof law and the rights of the people I
OL,12,Frepresent.
OL,14,F"I was also concerned that the
OL,15,Ftransfer of PCC powers to a
OL,16,Frepresentative of the government,
OL,17,Fwould lead to more cuts, more chaos
OL,18,Fand more crime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
