OL,3,CWest Midlands Police Commissioner wins
OL,4,Clegal challenge against power transfer
OL,6,F"The Home Secretary acknowledged that
OL,7,Fhe and the Mayor had previously failed
OL,8,Fto act in accordance with the law, by
OL,9,Ffailing to carry out a public
OL,10,Fconsultation and apply the relevant
OL,11,Fstatutory criteria.
OL,13,F"It defies belief that they had
OL,14,Ffarcically, inexplicably and
OL,15,Fincompetently failed to read and
OL,16,Funderstand their own legislation, that
OL,17,Fthey themselves had specifically
OL,18,Fpassed only weeks before, to remove
OL,19,Fthe need for a democratic mandate in
OL,20,Fthe West Midlands.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
