OL,3,CWest Midlands Police Commissioner wins
OL,4,Clegal challenge against power transfer
OL,6,F"It was only following legal action,
OL,7,Fsuccessfully challenging and holding
OL,8,Fthem to account, that they were forced
OL,9,Finto a humiliating climbdown and a
OL,10,Fbelated public consultation was
OL,11,Flaunched at all.
OL,13,F"Having already acted unlawfully and
OL,14,Fundertaken a public consultation, they
OL,15,Fthen also ignored the outcome. It was
OL,16,Ftherefore entirely right and proper
OL,17,Fthat I brought the claim for Judicial
OL,18,FReview, to ensure that the Home
OL,19,FSecretary and the Mayor had finally
OL,20,Funderstood their legal obligations and
OL,21,Fwere acting in accordance with the law.
