OL,6,F"The court has determined that the
OL,7,F11th hour, last minute, panic driven,
OL,8,Fconsultation launched by the Home
OL,9,FSecretary, was unlawful.
OL,11,F"The judge found that the consultation
OL,12,Fwas "not sufficient", "perfunctory"
OL,13,Fand required respondents to go on a
OL,14,F"treasure hunt" to obtain relevant
OL,15,Finformation. Ultimately it "misses the
OL,16,Fpoint of a consultation exercise".
