OL,6,F"The Home Secretary and the Mayor have
OL,7,Fwasted everyone's time and tax payers'
OL,8,Fmoney. In addition, they have been
OL,9,Fresponsible for causing incalculable
OL,10,Fdistraction and disruption, for West
OL,11,FMidlands Police, the Office of the
OL,12,FPolice and Crime Commissioner, the
OL,13,FCombined Authority and local election
OL,14,Fofficials, not to mention the
OL,15,Funcertainty it has created for the
OL,16,Fgeneral public of the West Midlands.
