OL,6,F"I am pleased that the Mayor's
OL,7,Fcynical, divisive, unnecessary and
OL,8,Fundemocratic, attempted hostile
OL,9,Ftakeover of PCC powers has been
OL,10,Fdefeated.
OL,12,F"I trust that we can now all
OL,13,Fconcentrate on what matters most to
OL,14,Fthe people of the West Midlands, which
OL,15,Fis ensuring that we all work together
OL,16,Fin partnership, to prevent, tackle and
OL,17,Freduce crime".
OL,19,FWest Midlands Mayor Andy Street said:
OL,20,F"My reaction is one of incredible
OL,21,Fdisappointment.
